  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to find out how effective lifestyle modification group therapy
      is on reducing body weight when compared to usual care in individuals with schizophrenia
      and/or schizoaffective disorder.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
